snippet.title: PHOBOS Project - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
PHOBOS Project is a first-person adventure exploring the depths of psychological horror. In this experiment you have to find a way out and keep your sanity level up through different hostile environments. Face your dread and try to find the source of the nightmare.

PHOBOS Project will be available on Steam on October 24, 2022. Feel free to add it to your wishlist !
Link : https://store.steampowered.com/app/20...
